---

layout: post
rulenumber: 14
title:  "Avoid partially duplicated microflows"
characteristic: Maintainability
impact_prio: 3
effort_prio: 3


---

**Why**
Avoid the exact duplication of microflows as duplicated significantly decrease the maintainability.

**How to fix**
Make use of sub-microflows if the same functionality is being used more than once instead of creatind duplicates of the microflow.
